886
01:01:25,098 --> 01:01:27,308
Hey, Soo-jin. It's me.

887
01:01:27,392 --> 01:01:30,353
Just letting you know
Mom can't come to your house tomorrow.

888
01:01:31,104 --> 01:01:32,897
Hey, don't you dare call me!

889
01:01:45,576 --> 01:01:46,619
Seriously!

890
01:01:48,121 --> 01:01:48,996
So tired of this.

891
01:01:56,713 --> 01:01:57,547
Mom.

892
