Thank you.

895
01:02:05,471 --> 01:02:10,017
Mom, it's about time we treated ourselves
to a night at a place like this.

896
01:02:10,101 --> 01:02:12,228
We'll get some sun in the morning,

897
01:02:12,812 --> 01:02:15,773
take a walk, and eat food
